{{Quote|Say, if you are into music you'll want to check out 'The Soundmound'! It usually has the best shows!|[[Mirax Terrik Horn|Mirax Terrik]], to [[Isplourrdacartha Estillo]]|<ref name="Star Wars: X-Wing Rogue Squadron: The Phantom Affair">''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Rogue Squadron: The Phantom Affair]]''</ref>}}
'''The Soundmound''' was an establishment on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Mrlsst/Legends|Mrlsst]] that served drinks and [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]] and was considered the best place to listen to music. This local was so well equipped, that it even had twelve different brands of ice. The band [[Ghost Jedi]] performed there in [[Hologram/Legends|holo]].

[[Koyi Komad]] was serving drinks in Soundmound, before she joined [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]], and it was there that she met Squadron's members for the first time.

